docs.text:
RevJS - Rev-up your data-driven JS app development!


RevJS is a suite of JavaScript modules, designed to speed up development of
data-driven applications.


This is achieved by removing the need for boilerplate 
Database
, 
API
 and

User Interface
 code and allowing developers to focus on the data-model and
business logic, i.e. the "important bits" of your application!
docs.title: What is RevJS?
